Package neqsim.process.equipment.compressor

Enum Class DriverType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<DriverType>
neqsim.process.equipment.compressor.DriverType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<DriverType>, Constable
public enum DriverType extends Enum<DriverType> implements Serializable
Enum representing different types of compressor drivers.

Each driver type has different characteristics for power delivery, efficiency, and response time.

Version:
1.0
Author:
esol

  • Enum Constant Details

    • ELECTRIC_MOTOR

      public static final DriverType ELECTRIC_MOTOR
      Electric motor driver. Fast response, constant torque, high efficiency at rated speed.

    • VFD_MOTOR

      public static final DriverType VFD_MOTOR
      Variable frequency drive electric motor. Allows continuous speed variation with high efficiency.

    • GAS_TURBINE

      public static final DriverType GAS_TURBINE
      Gas turbine driver. Variable speed, power dependent on ambient conditions.

    • STEAM_TURBINE

      public static final DriverType STEAM_TURBINE
      Steam turbine driver. Variable speed, power from steam supply.

    • RECIPROCATING_ENGINE

      public static final DriverType RECIPROCATING_ENGINE
      Reciprocating engine driver. High efficiency, limited speed range.

    • EXPANDER_DRIVE

      public static final DriverType EXPANDER_DRIVE
      Direct drive from process expander. No external power required.
